headline: Dow Jones Futures: Will Markets Hold With Trump Tariffs Set To Top Liberation Day Highs?
summary: The stock market held near highs last week as Trump tariffs continued Saturday. Inflation, earnings loom. Google, AMD are near buy points.

headline: History Says These 3 Stocks Could Be Big Winners in the Second Half
summary: Nvidia, Advanced Micro Devices, and Tesla have all been phenomenal growth stocks to own over the years.  Companies are continuing to post strong results.  As long as that's the case, there may still be plenty of bullishness in the markets for the foreseeable future.

headline: Dow Jones Futures: Stocks Hold Up Amid Trump Tariffs, But Growth Woes Worrisome; Google, AMD Near Buy Points
summary: The stock market fell for the week but held near highs amid Trump tariffs. Inflation and earnings reports will be in focus. Google and AMD are near buy points.
